comments: Redick (PHI) lifts his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.  The official is looking for any possible illegal contact and does not pick up the pivot foot movement.
Lowry (TOR) makes marginal contact to Redick's (PHI) arm on the perimeter.
Redick (PHI) engages with Lowry (TOR) and releases from the contact without dislodging Lowry from his defensive position.
RLS shows Gasol (TOR) makes contact to Butler's (PHI) arm that affects his jump shot attempt.
Embiid (PHI) establishes himself in a legal guarding position, jumping vertically and absorbing the contact at the end of Leonard's (TOR) drive.
Embiid (PHI) makes contact with Green (TOR) as he slightly extends his forearm into his path, but does not affect his ability to defend.
Simmons (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Siakam's (TOR) path and absorbs the contact during the off-ball screen.
Siakam (TOR) makes clean contact to the ball while defending the pass in the post.
Harris (PHI) places an arm to Lowry's (TOR) front during the drive, but the contact is marginal and does not affect his SQBR.
Gasol (TOR) makes incidental contact with Embiid (PHI) that does not affect his ability to get to the loose ball.
Embiid (PHI) establishes himself in a legal guarding position, jumping vertically and absorbing the contact from Siakam (TOR).
Lowry (TOR) places an arm against Butler (PHI) but does not dislodge him from his rebounding position.
Embiid (PHI) disengages from the contact with Green (TOR) and does not push him during the pick.
Gasol (TOR) slides his arm across Embiid's (PHI) back but the contact is marginal and does not affect his SQBR.
Embiid (PHI) maintains his pivot foot during his spin move towards the basket.
Gasol (TOR) makes marginal contact to Embiid's (PHI) off-arm that does not affect his play at the basket.
Ennis III (PHI) briefly places an arm around Gasol (TOR) but immediately slides it off.
Harris (PHI) is in a legal guarding position and Lowry (TOR) loses control of the ball on his own at the start of his drive.
Leonard (TOR) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Simmons (PHI) and Gasol (TOR) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Green (TOR) commits a take foul on Harris (PHI).
